<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>نِكَاتٌ لُغَوِيَّة<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">مِن:</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>مِنْ في اللُّغَةِ قَدْ تَكُونُ لِبَيَانِ الجِنس؛<span class="c5"> كَقَوْلِهِمْ:</span> بَابٌ مِن حَدِيد ٠<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَقَدْ تَكُونُ للاِبْتِدَاء؛<span class="c5"> كَقَوْلِهِمْ:</span> خَرَجْت مِنْ مَكَّةَ إِلىَ يَثْرِب ٠<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وَلِلاِسْتِغْرَاقِ؛<span class="c5"> كَقَوْلِهِمْ:</span> اقْتَلَعَهَا مِنْ جُذُورِهَا ٠<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">الإِضَافَةُ:</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">إِضَافَةُ مِلْك:</span> كَقَوْلِنَا عَبْدُ اللهِ وَسَمَاءُ الله ٠<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>°*°*°*°*°*°*°*°*°*°*°*°*°*°*°*°*°*°*°*°*°*°*°*°*°*°*°*°*°*°*°*°<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>